quran[24]{c,v,t,f}:
  53,45,"Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó dá ẹ̀dá ní oríṣi méjì, ọkùnrin àti obìnrin,<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ẹ̀dá ènìyàn ni èròǹgbà nínú āyah yìí, kì í ṣe ẹ̀dá mìíràn. Āyah 46 l’ó fi èyí rinlẹ̀."
  53,46,"láti ara àtọ̀ nígbà tí wọ́n bá dà á sínú àpòlùkẹ́.",""
  53,47,"Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó máa ṣe ìṣẹ̀dá ìkẹ́yìn fún àjíǹde,",""
  53,48,"Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó ń fún ẹ̀dá ní ọrọ̀ dúkìá, Ó sì ń ta ẹ̀dá ní òṣì.",""
  53,49,"Dájúdájú Òun sì ni Olúwa ìràwọ̀ Ṣi‘rọ̄ (tí wọ́n sọ di òrìṣà).",""
  53,50,"Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó pa ìran ‘Ād rẹ́, àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́;",""
  53,51,"àti ìran Thamūd, kò sì ṣẹ́ wọn kù;",""
  53,52,"àti ìjọ Nūh tó ṣíwájú (wọn), dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ alábòsí jùlọ, wọ́n sì tayọ ẹnu-ààlà jùlọ;",""
  53,53,"àti ìlú tó dojú bolẹ̀ (ìlú Ànábì Lūt), Allāhu ló yẹ̀ ẹ́ lulẹ̀ (láti òkè).",""
  53,54,"Ohun tó bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀ bò wọ́n mọ́lẹ̀.",""
  53,55,"Nítorí náà, èwo nínú ìdẹ̀ra Olúwa rẹ ni ìwọ (ènìyàn) ń jà níyàn?",""
  53,56,"Èyí ni ìkìlọ̀ kan nínú àwọn ìkìlọ̀ àkọ́kọ́.",""
  53,57,"Ohun tó súnmọ́<sup>1</sup> súnmọ́.","[1] “Ohun tó súnmọ́” jẹ́ ọ̀kan nínú àwọn orúkọ fún Ọjọ́ àjíǹde."
  53,58,"Lẹ́yìn Allāhu, kò sí ẹni tó lè tú gbèdéke Àkókò náà jáde.<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ó tún túmọ̀ sí pé, “Lẹ́yìn Allāhu, kò sí ẹni tó lè gbé ìdààmú ọjọ́ Àkókò náà kúrò fún ẹ̀dá.”"
  53,59,"Ṣé ọ̀rọ̀ yìí l’ó ń ṣe yín ní kàyéfì?",""
  53,60,"Ẹ̀ ń rẹ́rìn-ín, ẹ kò sì sunkún!",""
  53,61,"Afọ́nú-fọ́ra ni yín.",""
  53,62,"Nítorí náà, ẹ forí kanlẹ̀ fún Allāhu, kí ẹ jọ́sìn (fún Un).",""
  54,1,"Àkókò náà súnmọ́. Òṣùpá sì là pẹrẹgẹdẹ (sí méjì).<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìyẹn ṣẹlẹ̀ ní àsìkò Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - nígbà tí àwọn ọ̀ṣẹbọ bèèrè fún àmì ìyanu lọ́wọ́ rẹ̀."
  54,2,"Tí wọ́n bá rí àmì kan, wọ́n máa gbúnrí. Wọn yó sí wí pé: “Idán kan tó máa parẹ́ (ni èyí).”<sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún “sihrun mustamirr” idán kan tó lágbára (ni èyí)."
  54,3,"Wọ́n pè é ní irọ́. Wọ́n sì tẹ̀lé ìfẹ́-inú wọn. Gbogbo iṣẹ́ ẹ̀dá sì máa jókòó tì í lọ́rùn. <sup>1</sup>","[1] Ìtúmọ̀ mìíràn fún “wa kullu ’amrin mustaƙirr” Gbogbo ìṣe ẹ̀dá ló ní ìkángun."
  54,4,"Dájúdájú wáàsí tí ó ń kọ aburú<sup>1</sup> wà nínú àwọn ìró tó dé bá wọn.","[1] “Muzdajar” wáàsí tó le tó kún fún ìṣẹ̀rùbà àti àpẹ̀ẹrẹ ìjìyà tó ṣẹlẹ̀ sí àwọn ẹni àkọ́kọ́ nínú àwọn ọ̀tá òdodo."
  54,5,"(al-Ƙur’ān sì ni) ọgbọ́n tó péye pátápátá; ṣùgbọ́n àwọn ìkìlọ̀ náà kò rọ̀ wọ́n lọ́rọ̀.",""
  54,6,"Ṣẹ́rí kúrò ní ọ̀dọ̀ wọn. Ní ọjọ́ tí olùpèpè yóò pèpè fún kiní kan tí ẹ̀mí kórira (ìyẹn, Àjíǹde),",""
